    "created_at": "2016-07-25T08:06:48Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-07-25T08:06:48Z",
    "body": "Using `[NSCursor currentSystemCursor]` has to initialize `NSApplication` because it needs to access system theme settings, it should be totally fine to call `sharedApplication` if you don't mind the small cost of calling.\n\nThe renderer process appears not responding because the message loop doesn't pump NSRunLoop.\n\nInitializing the whole UI stuff in renderer process is bad for performance, so we will not do it.\n"
  },
